## Declaration of Compliance { #conformance }

Sources for which one of the keywords below is mentioned are in partially or fully compliant with the requirements of the Delegated Regulation to ITS Directive [2010/40/EU](https://eur-lex.europa.eu/eli/dir/2010/40) amended by [2023/2661](https://eur-lex.europa.eu/eli/dir/2023/2661). See the referenced declarations of conformity.

|Label | Description| File|
|-|-|-|
